ActMuseums Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Canadian Heritage of BRIAN PAUL MCBAY of Vancouver, British Columbia, to be a trustee of the Board of Trustees of the National Gallery of Canada, to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of G. Howard Kroon, whose term has expired.
